      "updated": 1748973150027,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Ori region variant is not age-related.\n2. Ref Allele of C/A mutated, is light strand variant.\n3. Ref Allele of G/T mutated, is heavy strand variant.\n4. Other region, A>G and heavy chain C>T is  age related variants",
      "fontSize": 19.970703124999993,
      "fontFamily": 5,
