      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Ori region variant is not age-related.\n2. Ref Allele of C/A mutated, is light strand variant.\n3. Ref Allele of G/T mutated, is heavy strand variant.\n4. Other region, A>G and heavy chain C>T is  age related variants",
